292
00:13:54,168 --> 00:13:55,288
Deep In The Bustle

293
00:13:55,567 --> 00:13:56,567
has plenty of resources.

294
00:13:57,168 --> 00:13:58,528
It depends on if you're willing

295
00:13:58,528 --> 00:13:59,807
to join hands and move forward

296
00:14:00,008 --> 00:14:01,168
to move Danding State

297
00:14:01,168 --> 00:14:02,567
and even the entire nation

298
00:14:02,567 --> 00:14:04,288
to a higher level.

299
00:14:05,807 --> 00:14:06,528
Zheng,

300
00:14:06,648 --> 00:14:07,727
process this gradually.

301
00:14:07,967 --> 00:14:08,768
I'll

302
00:14:09,008 --> 00:14:10,720
tell you how

303
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,768
he escaped from the factory that day.

304
00:14:13,248 --> 00:14:14,248
That was

305
00:14:15,048 --> 00:14:17,888
absolutely thrilling!

306
00:14:25,248 --> 00:14:28,922
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

307
00:14:29,221 --> 00:14:32,412
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

308
00:14:34,244 --> 00:14:37,920
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

309
00:14:38,414 --> 00:14:41,344
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

310
00:14:42,684 --> 00:14:46,464
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

311
00:14:46,638 --> 00:14:50,272
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

312
00:14:51,534 --> 00:14:55,221
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

313
00:14:55,859 --> 00:15:00,974
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

314
00:15:01,678 --> 00:15:05,812
♪I feel guilty♪

315
00:15:06,382 --> 00:15:10,126
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

316
00:15:10,990 --> 00:15:14,433
♪Even in tears♪

317
00:15:15,182 --> 00:15:19,278
♪It doesn't matter♪

318
00:15:19,278 --> 00:15:23,101
♪We embrace in dreams♪

319
00:15:23,950 --> 00:15:27,388
♪I let down all my defenses♪

320
00:15:28,622 --> 00:15:32,096
♪Though the story has its end♪

321
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:40,288
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
